---
title: Honey-Soy Turkey Meatball Stir Fry with Rice and Sriracha
description: It's a mixed veggie bonanza! Carrots, bok choy and onions get tossed with turkey meatballs and a glossy, umami-packed honey-soy sauce. Fluffy jasmine rice makes the perfect pedestal for these fine flavours to rest on!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saute-de-legumes-et-de-boulettes-de-dinde-au-miel-et-au-soja-493aee1d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/honey-soy-turkey-meatball-stir-fry-628b276dbd952056f80eccb4-40080b11.pdf
